# Branch and pull request workflow

See **[CONTRIBUTING.md](../../CONTRIBUTING.md)** and **`00-project-always.mdc`** (push gate + `gh pr checks --watch` + auto-merge defaults).

- Stay current with `main`: `git fetch` + rebase onto `origin/main` before push when appropriate.
- Default PR: **draft** (`gh pr create --draft`) until ready; resolve conflicts before merge.
- After creating or updating a PR branch: **`gh pr checks <number> --watch`** unless the user said not to watch.
- When submitting for merge: **`gh pr merge <number> --auto --squash`** unless the user disabled auto-merge.
- Post-merge deploy (Cloud Run): optional `gcloud` verification on a later pass — CONTRIBUTING.

If `gh` is unavailable, say so and use the web UI equivalents.
